      "text": "Stafford Beer, Brain of the firm: the managerial cybernetics of organization, 2d ed (Chichester [Eng.] ; New York: J. Wiley, 1981), p. 64: Both the neuron and the manager have one really basic task to perform: to [[decide]]. "
